metadata.name: Many Faces Pt. 1
metadata.description:
Many Faces - Set 1 - A Music/Art fusion

Inspired by the amazing @ilyakazakov 

What is Many Faces?  
Many Faces is an art series project created by Domino — hand drawn faces and eyes that are accompanied by CC0 music. Each face is drawn by Domino, with the music personally made per each face. 

Each art piece is enhanced to 4k to ensure quality — while holding the NFT you are granted full rights and access to the music that accompanies It to be used for whatever your heart desires. 


What’s with the burn? 

Be ready to burn your Many Faces OE to get a single Face! 

1 OE = 1 FACE 

Holding ALL Faces in a Set grants you access to a physical poster + a unique airdrop. 

Holders can choose the face that best suits them. Burn pages will post once burn date is set



Will there be Rare Sets?? 

YES!!!!!!!

At a later date a RARE Many Faces set will drop. In order to mint a Rare Face, Super Rare Face or Ultra Rare Face It looks like this: 

9 Many Faces OE = Ultra Rare Face  
5 Many Faces OE = Super Rare Faces 
3 Many Faces OE = Rare Face 



How Many Sets of Many Faces will there be? 

For now, the future is Unknown.. I can guarantee the Rare set for set 1 is coming. If there is demand, the faces will begin to show themselves.
